title: Community Day of Services Director Interview
Application Type: I applied online. I interviewed at Project Homeless Connect (San Francisco, CA) in Nov 2019
Interview Descriptions: I sat down with the CEO and the COO and they took turns asking me questions  that were related to my current job and experience. It was friendly and casual.
Interview Questions: What experience did I have managing volunteers?

title: Program Associate Interview
Application Type: I applied through other source. I interviewed at Project Homeless Connect
Interview Descriptions: 3 interviews, 2 in person. Be able to show passion for nonprofit and why homelessness is an issue that is important to you. Salary is average for nonprofit orgs and you have some city employee benefits.
Interview Questions: Where do you see yourself in 5 years?
